===========
1.
	|x(0)|			|1	1			1		 |	|X'_0|
	|x(1)|	=	1/p	|1	e^(iwk)	e^(i2wk)|	|X'_1|
	|x(2)|			|1	e^(i2wk)	e^(i4wk)|	|X'_2|

	|1	1			1		 |	|x(0)|		|X'_0|
	|1	e^(-iwk)	e^(-i2wk)|	|x(1)|	=	|X'_1|
	|1	e^(-i2wk)	e^(-i4wk)|	|x(2)|		|X'_2|
2.
	AB=I_3
	x(n)--DTFT-->X(w)
	Claim:
	nx(n) --DTFT--> i dX(w)/dw

	\int_(-pi)^(pi) i dX(w)/dw e^(iwn) dw
	=\int_(-pi)^(pi) dX(w)/dw e^(iwn+i \pi/2) dw
	=X(pi) e^(i pi n+i \pi/2)+X(-pi) e^(i -pi n+i \pi/2)
	=X(pi) e^(i pi n+i \pi/2)+X(-pi) e^(i -pi n+i \pi/2)

